WEBVTT

00:00:00.865 --> 00:00:02.587
I would like to invite you

00:00:02.611 --> 00:00:04.317
to come along on a visit

00:00:04.341 --> 00:00:05.730
to a dark continent.

00:00:06.399 --> 00:00:08.013
It is the continent hidden

00:00:08.037 --> 00:00:10.089
under the surface of the earth.

00:00:10.113 --> 00:00:12.406
It is largely unexplored,

00:00:12.430 --> 00:00:15.113
poorly understood,
and the stuff of legends.

00:00:15.137 --> 00:00:17.975
But it is made also of dramatic landscapes

00:00:17.999 --> 00:00:20.494
like this huge underground chamber,

00:00:20.518 --> 00:00:25.359
and it is rich with surprising
biological and mineralogical worlds.

00:00:26.149 --> 00:00:30.975
Thanks to the efforts of intrepid voyagers
in the last three centuries --